stories.title: AUSTRALIA v ENGLAND 1986-87
stories.subTitle: World Series Cup - Second Final Match
stories.summary: O'Donnell, driving DeFreitas twice for six, made a valiant attempt to take the finals to a third match by scoring 40 off 27 balls; but England's 187 for nine proved out of range
